trans-unit.source: Defines the configuration element for a peer resolver.
Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Configuration.PeerResolverElement"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Configuration.PeerResolverElement"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Gets the configuration element for this peer resolver if it is a custom peer resolver implementation.
trans-unit.target: Henter konfigurasjonselementet for denne node-Løsningsprogram hvis den er en egendefinert node Løsningsprogrammet implementering.

trans-unit.source: This property contains an instance of <xref:System.ServiceModel.Configuration.PeerCustomResolverElement> if the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Configuration.PeerResolverElement.Mode%2A> property is set to <xref:System.ServiceModel.PeerResolvers.PeerResolverMode>.
trans-unit.target: Denne egenskapen inneholder en forekomst av <xref:System.ServiceModel.Configuration.PeerCustomResolverElement>Hvis <xref:System.ServiceModel.Configuration.PeerResolverElement.Mode%2A>egenskapen er satt til <xref:System.ServiceModel.PeerResolvers.PeerResolverMode>.</xref:System.ServiceModel.PeerResolvers.PeerResolverMode> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Configuration.PeerResolverElement.Mode%2A> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Configuration.PeerCustomResolverElement>

trans-unit.source: <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Configuration.PeerCustomResolverElement"></xref> that contains the configuration element for the peer resolver if it is a custom peer resolver implementation.
trans-unit.target: <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Configuration.PeerCustomResolverElement"></xref>som inneholder konfigurasjonselementet for node-Løsningsprogram hvis den er en egendefinert node Løsningsprogrammet implementering.

trans-unit.source: Gets and sets the type of the peer resolver represented by this configuration element.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir typen av node løseren som representeres av denne konfigurasjonselementet.

trans-unit.source: <xref href="System.ServiceModel.PeerResolvers.PeerResolverMode"></xref> enumeration value that specifies the type of peer resolvder represented by this configuration element.
trans-unit.target: <xref href="System.ServiceModel.PeerResolvers.PeerResolverMode"></xref>opplistingsverdi som angir hvilken type node resolvder representert av denne konfigurasjonselementet.

trans-unit.source: Gets and sets the referral policy for peer resolvers configured with this element.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir henvisning-policyen for node-omgjørere som er konfigurert med dette elementet.

trans-unit.source: <xref href="System.ServiceModel.PeerResolvers.PeerReferralPolicy"></xref> that specifies the referral policy for peer resolvers configured with this element.
trans-unit.target: <xref href="System.ServiceModel.PeerResolvers.PeerReferralPolicy"></xref>som angir policyen som referanse for node-omgjørere som er konfigurert med dette elementet.
